{"title":"Savage","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":64,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/tyvj-2308","statement":[{"title":"","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"\n# \n\n \n # 题目描述 \n<p>\n<img border=\"0\" src=\"/source/joyoi/tyvj-2308/img/aHR0cDovL3d3dy5qb3lvaS5jbi9wcm9ibGVtL3R5dmotMjMwOC9wcm9ibGVtc19pbWFnZXMvMjY4NC8xNDA3LmpwZw==.jpg\">\r<br></p> \n\n \n # 输入格式 \n<p>\n第1行为一个整数N(1<=N<=15)，即野人的数目。第2行到第N+1每行为三个整数Ci, Pi, Li (1<=Ci,Pi<=100, 0<=Li<=106 )，表示每个野人所住的初始洞穴编号，每年走过的洞穴数及寿命值。\r<br>\r<br></p> \n\n \n # 输出格式 \n<p>\n仅包含一个数M，即最少可能的山洞数。输入数据保证有解，且M不大于106。\r<br>\r<br>\r<br></p> "},{"title":"# 样例数据","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"<style>\n        table,table tr th, table tr td { border:1px solid #0094ff; }\n        table { width: 200px; min-height: 25px; line-height: 25px; text-align: center; border-collapse: collapse;}   \n    </style>\n<table>\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td>输入样例</td>\n\t\t<td>输出样例</td>\n\t</tr>\n<tr><td>3\r\n1     3      4\r\n2     7      3\r\n3     2      1\r\n\r\n</td><td>6\r\n\r\n该样例对应于题目描述中的例子。</td></tr></table>\n\n"}]}